From 55608f00924660549fe8507c4755dcc29b4d2e59 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Thu, 16 Apr 2026 03:35:35 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: surface MCP notifications/message to the model's
 conversation

Currently, when an MCP server sends a notifications/message log
notification, Codex CLI routes it to Rust tracing only. The model
never sees it. This commit adds plumbing for info+ level notifications
to be forwarded as McpServerLogMessage events through the existing
tx_event channel to the agent loop.

Closes #17543
Refs #18056, #16060, #17501
